Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}集齊所有卡牌之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那並不是結束 而是開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是通往結束的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}庫洛魔法使 透明牌篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在直擊透明牌核心的後半部分開始之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天為大家帶來總集篇 回顧一下之前的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}差不多到時間了 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.46,0:01:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫木之本櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在是友枝中學的國一學生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我正想去叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.69,0:01:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}國中的校服也很適合你 很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對吧 桃矢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怪獸也要穿衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}才不是普通衣服 這是校服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不否定怪獸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥你就算成了大學生也還像個小孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也是 上了國中還是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 該出門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我出門了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}國中的新生活讓小櫻無比興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.84,0:01:57.18,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}升上了國中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.89,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}如果你們有什麼不懂的或者有什麼煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:03.81,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以來找我這個班導師 或者是副班導師森老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能坐知世旁邊真好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這時 出現在小櫻面前的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}香港那邊的手續和事情終於辦完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以後就可以一直在友枝町了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以後要一直在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這隻熊不是小櫻送給小鬼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是小鬼回香港的前一天你熬夜做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼會在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你送我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣你回家要繞遠路了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為我想和你多待一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也一直把這隻名叫小櫻的小熊帶在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我覺得它和製作者分開會很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讓它在你身邊待一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}叫小狼的小熊也會很想見它的製作者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我們就交換一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很久沒用這個了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 這樣才好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那天晚上 小櫻做了一個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}卡牌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}緊急情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我變身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.45,0:05:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我昨晚做了個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}透明的卡牌漂浮著 然後碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我很擔心 打開書一看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夢裡只是卡牌碎了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有個人站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}像個斗篷一樣 臉和身體都被遮了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夢境反覆重現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以及在夢中得到的新鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻身邊也發生了異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不知道 感覺不到任何氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 這不是普通的風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 用卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}它們都變透明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}難道說這個鑰匙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}變成魔杖了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}用原來的咒文肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為了使用這個魔杖的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}新的卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}透明的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 這樣看卻看不到另一面的圖案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只能感覺到你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可是 為什麼友枝町又發生了這種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「SIEGE」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「包圍」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在夢之鑰匙和透明卡牌的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻再次開始收集卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「反射」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「REFLECT」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.38,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都回座位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天給大家介紹一位新同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}詩之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫詩之本秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你以前在香港的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 來日本之前 我住在香港
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}香港之前是法國 再之前是德國
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你說還去過義大利和英國吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我要去找老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要去老師辦公室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}話說回來 我們倆挺像的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫木之本櫻 你叫詩之本秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}總感覺很像 特別是姓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻同學 我想和你成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請多多關照 小櫻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好可愛的小兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.07,0:10:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我一直都帶著它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 不知道能不能帶到學校去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}賞花的時候我也想帶上來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是怕你們覺得我幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們學校可以帶玩偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家一定都會覺得很可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小桃你好 我們好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我才是 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是吧 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}收集的透明牌越來越多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然而 謎團卻越來越深
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夢怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還是和原來一樣 我不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一個和我身高差不多的人站在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 還有聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聲音嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}滴答滴答 鐘的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有巨大的齒輪和指針
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗你是走路去學校的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 因為很近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.87,0:12:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你家是什麼樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是獨棟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那裡以前好像住著和我一樣大的 從英國來的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有你家的照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有 有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然是艾利歐家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感覺好久沒來過這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有點緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}歡迎你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你招待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我很高興你們能來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}感謝你們今天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不不 我們才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是海渡 從小就一直照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫尤那·D·海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}負責照顧秋穗的生活起居
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}打攪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我泡了你們送的櫻花茶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是優雅的動作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟我每天都要做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}點心 飯菜和便當都是他親手做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟這就是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個 吃完蛋糕我想帶你們去一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這些全部都是你的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}與其說是我的 不如說是我的家族收集來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也非常喜歡書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有一本特別想要的書 所以來到了日本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗 你剛剛說有你喜歡的書對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咦 沒有書名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封面上沒有寫書名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這本書叫「愛麗絲夢遊鐘錶王國」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「愛麗絲夢遊鐘錶王國」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是「愛麗絲夢遊仙境」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然與「愛麗絲夢遊仙境」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和「愛麗絲鏡中奇遇」 不是同一個作者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封面也好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個時鐘的圖案…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個時鐘好像在哪裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}到底是在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在擁有的卡牌都在這了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發生一些事情 然後你就能收服卡牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}確實和收服庫洛牌的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 還是不知道為什麼會發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要是有什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你這什麼眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 時間差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我該出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了 今天是個好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}第一次和小狼出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他們來到了水族館 也就是以前收服「水」的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是爸爸在大學拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和你的好夥伴一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他還這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大哥哥和大姐姐的臉好紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他們關係真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.08,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}關係好？ 那為什麼會臉紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:47.50,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼會臉紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}走 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我在 在和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和我什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和庫洛牌的時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}跟之前的「水」一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我也要像那時一樣 開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}上次也是這樣進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我很在意這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這不是和收服「水」的時候一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是水？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}冰華招來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}就是現在 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}無主之物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以夢之杖 為吾之力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}固著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}目前能察覺卡牌氣息的只有小櫻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你怎麼了 知世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 說不定是我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}告訴我吧 說不定會是什麼線索
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個「迷宮」和「打盹」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和庫洛牌的「迷」和「眠」引發的事件是不是很相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有好幾張卡牌都跟庫洛牌很像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「水源」很像「水」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「飛翔」很像「翔」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}以前收集的卡牌和新卡牌有相同之處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}隱藏在其中的秘密是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.73,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們這是要回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我剛去買了東西 準備回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉 沒來得及問候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你好 我是負責照顧秋穗小姐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我叫尤那·D·海渡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻身邊有擁有魔力的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻和一個轉學生關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那人是負責照顧那個轉學生的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}尤那·D…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我並不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 如果這個D是那個D稱號的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}D稱號？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是英國的某個魔法師協會授予最高位魔法師的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 魔法師會做出暴露自己身份的舉動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.92,0:22:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可能他已經強大到了就算暴露也沒關係的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.94,0:22:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}睡得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過 我又做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又做夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我站在高處 看著一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還是不知道那個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.33,0:22:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是今天我知道原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.84,0:22:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還說了「我想要你手中的東西」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.06,0:22:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又是這個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還是想要鑰匙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.34,0:23:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也不知道為什麼會在夢中得到這個鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:23:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.86,0:24:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻的夢和秋穗的夢有著相同之處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.69,0:24:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夢中之人的真實身份究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼的表妹莓鈴從香港來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.62,0:24:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}面對這突如其來的驚喜 小櫻十分開心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且 莓鈴還要住在小櫻家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.71,0:24:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下集 小櫻和剛回來的莓鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.09,0:24:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}
